(299, 62, 'introduction_introduction_content', 'Set in the heart of Newmarket, this charming guest house dates back to the 18th century and offers free Wi-Fi in public areas. Newmarket Racecourse is 5 minutes’ drive away, and it is a 15-minute drive to the centre of Cambridge.\r\n\r\nThe prestigious horse sales arena, Tattersalls, can be reached in less than 10 minutes’ walk from Crown Rooms Newmarket. The Rookery Shopping Centre is 5 minutes’ walk away, and Bury St Edmunds is only 25 minutes’ drive from the building.\r\n\r\nAccommodation at Crown Rooms is cosy, with simple décor and an en suite bathroom with free toiletries. Features include a flat-screen TV and tea and coffee making facilities.'),
